166
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam na kraju godine, tek sam tada skužio,

167
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] shvatio upozna ljude, ono, ima udruga studentata Cetinske krajine,

168
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:39,000
