1193
01:13:01,739 --> 01:13:04,020
[SPEAKER_01] Lakše udomiti ili posvojiti?

1194
01:13:04,699 --> 01:13:05,520
[SPEAKER_01] Udomiti, vjerojatno.

1195
01:13:05,520 --> 01:13:06,739
