1224
01:13:36,600 --> 01:13:37,819
[SPEAKER_00] Tek kasnije ulaziš.

1225
01:13:37,819 --> 01:13:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, ok.

1226
01:13:38,279 --> 01:13:39,359
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo te prolaze,

1227
